actions.message:
**TreeTopHost** is a brand new web hosting solution established in October 2020.
TreeTopHost is dedicated to provide the best services to their clients, either premium or free!
Our starter plan help people to get started easily free of cost! And we never ask any payment information unless you choose premium plans. Premium plans are packed by more powerful tools and better server performance.
We offer REAL cPanel hosting for all accounts, which gets included with Automation like APIs, Jetbackup, Softaculous, Let's Encrypt and much more! Our premium plans are the cheapest of all and we know you will love us.
We also provide handy customer care support for everyone around! The most interactive way for support is via [forums](https://forums.treetophost.com).

For what are you waiting? Get started right now!

**Some Important Links**
[TreeTopHost Main Website](https://treetophost.com)
[TreeTopHost Discord Server](https://treetophost.com/discord)
[TreeTopHost cPanel](https://cpanel.treetophost.com/)
